content: On the other side, you'll find a stairway leading up to a long curved path in a large open room, with giant beams along the ceiling from which Puppet Spiders dangle. It's a good idea to pause here a moment, because there's a patrolling enemy who is a lot to deal with, you won't want to fight him with his friends.
